title: 285 22 "Obtain the 5 Keys! The Straw Hat Pirates vs. CP9!"Transliteration: "Itsutsu no Kage o Ubae! Mugiwara Ichimi Tai CP9" (Japanese:5つの鍵を奪え! 麦わら一味対CP9) Takahiro Imamura Koga Naoki November 12, 2006(2006-11-12)[32] January 25, 2015
transformers_text: 285 22 Obtain the 5 Keys The Straw Hat Pirates vs CP 9 Transliteration Its u tsu no K age o U bae Mugi war a Ichi mi Tai CP 9 Japanese 5 CP 9 Takahiro Imamura Koga Naoki November 12 2006 2006 11 12 32 January 25 2015 After emerging from the rubble caused by Rocket Man crashing into the Tower of Law the Straw Hats and Franky are greeted by the blabbermouth CP 9 agent Fuku rou as he reveals that Span dam has given CP 9 orders to execute the intruders Also explaining that Span dam and Lucci are taking Robin to the Gates of Justice Fuku rou adds that he and four other CP 9 members each possess a key that may unlock these a stone handcuffs on Robin As Luffy chases after Robin the Straw Hats and Franky pursue the keys and each encounter a CP 9 member At the same time Chimney and her pet rabbit Gon be accidentally find a secret passage and end up following Span dam and Lucci as they take Robin to the Gates of Justice
